item.title: I’m back!
item.description: I know that it’s been a while since I wrote a post! I haven’t been keeping up with my own goal to write something new at least every week. At first this was because I was on holidays and internet access was spotty at best. More recently I’ve been very busy at work and not had as much time for reflection. I wanted to call this out here to keep myself honest and to make a fresh commitment!
